      Methods in net.openhft.chronicle.common with parameters of type StatelessBuilder 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      B ChronicleHashBuilder.stateless(StatelessBuilder statelessBuilder)
      Specifies that hash containers, created by this builder, should be a stateless implementation, this stateless implementation will be referred to as a stateless client as it will not hold any of its own data locally, the stateless client will perform Remote Procedure Calls ( RPC ) to another ChronicleMap or ChronicleSet which we will refer to as the server.
